<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201104/38901af5cab74330aedefed3fa8b3b1a.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">（新闻来源：四川观察）</span></img></p>
